past.title: Introduction to Google Cloud Study Jam
past.description: Google Cloud is a cloud computing platform offered by Google, providing a suite of services for computing, storage, data analytics, machine learning, and more. A Google Cloud Study Jam is a hands-on learning event or workshop aimed at helping participants gain practical experience and skills in using Google Cloud services and tools.
